{"tid":2516861,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"話說大陸貓今日香港試業 會唔會有香港人幫襯","createTime":"2021-05-05T02:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T03:15:02.000Z","uid":181257,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d28d110510a149e018810ffa795b147b7cec0b79","tid":2516861,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:43:23.000Z","msg":"點解咁撚夠薑，呢個時候仲喺香港搞。到底係睇死香港人貪著數性格唔理大陸閪背景照幫襯，定一話香港真係咁多新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 老婆好鐘意上網買嘢，如果俾我知道佢上天貓買嘢<br />\n我一定經濟封鎖制裁佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0352b40b646d634d4e737693a1a2b73f1106e8c2","tid":2516861,"uid":181257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:45:59.000Z","msg":"好想睇到佢同順豐同一下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6b5ee68eb6160ae95748d9cc62380489921b6b","tid":2516861,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"阿里巴巴 （09988） 旗下「天貓香港」上線試業，本地電商平台龍頭HKTVmall母企香港電視 （01137） 連跌第五日，香港電視今日早段最多跌7.8%，低見9.58元，收報9.77元，跌6%。天貓香港周三起3日（5月5日至5月7日）全場免運費。<br />\n<br />\n天貓香港由原先淘寶天貓分拆而來，號稱現有2000品牌進駐，天貓淘寶港澳事業部負責人陳子堅表示，淘寶天貓在香港市場消費者用戶覆蓋非常大，活躍用戶數、訪問次數均明顯優於同業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFrom 經濟日報"},{"pid":"02c45ccb637ff97b68c5f6bbc987cc0bbd70427d","tid":2516861,"uid":333532,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"唔講政治既話，我覺得支那個天貓應該可以同hktv mall比得上，以前成日用hktv mall，但係宜家越黎越少用<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbed81cccd6061c8690ae29990bca1db749bc2af","tid":2516861,"uid":155289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021